<div id="main_content">
	<h2>UCF Celebrates Grand Opening of Bright House Networks Stadium</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By UCF Staff
		
		<span class="date">Updated Sept. 16, 2007</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 261px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/0/NE992/en_US/hittcrop.jpg" height="196" width="261"  /> 
			
